      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 9 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 9 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九，復自道，何其咎，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows its subject returning and pursuing his own course. What mistake should he fall into? There will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
