      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 9 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 9 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二，牽復，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows its subject, by the attraction (of the former line), returning (to the proper course). There will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
