      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 9 六四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 9 六四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四，有孚，血去惕出，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth SIX, divided, shows its subject possessed of sincerity. The danger of bloodshed is thereby averted, and his (ground for) apprehension dismissed. There will be no mistake.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
