      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 9 九五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 9 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五，有孚攣如，富以其鄰。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows its subject possessed of sincerity, and drawing others to unite with him. Rich in resources, he employs his neighbours (in the same cause with himself).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="yijing-009-xiao-xu__alignment-007">
